***Background of American Express***
_____
The name of the company is American Express.
The company was incorporated in 1850.
The comoany was founded by the same founders as wells fargo as well as John Butterfield.
The comoany originally was to change traditional banking by expanding sservices on new routes or strategically challenged routes that had not been done before.
American Express is publically funded with 107 billion dollars in market capitalization funding and financing.
